{"name": "django-admin-black", "metadata": {"name": "django-admin-black", "version": "1.0.15", "classifiers": ["Environment :: Web Environment", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Intended Audience :: System Administrators", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.2", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.4", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Topic :: Software Development", "Topic :: Software Development :: User Interfaces"], "home_page": "https://app-generator.dev/docs/products/django-libs/theme-black-dashboard.html", "license": "MIT License", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Modern template for Django Admin - Black Dashboard Design", "upload_time": 1734365745}, "documentation": ["# [Django Black Dashboard](https://app-generator.dev/docs/products/django-libs/theme-black-dashboard.html)\r\n\r\nModern template for **[Django Admin](https://app-generator.dev/docs/products/django-libs/theme-black-dashboard.html)**, Auth Pages (registration included) crafted on top of **Black Dashboard**, an open-source **Bootstrap** design.\r\n\r\n- [Django Admin Black](https://app-generator.dev/docs/products/django-libs/theme-black-dashboard.html) - Documentation & Support Links\r\n- [Django Black Dashboard](https://app-generator.dev/product/black-dashboard/django/) - The product that uses the library\r\n- [Getting Started with Django](https://app-generator.dev/docs/technologies/django/index.html) - Learn how to code **Django** Projects\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n## **Features**\r\n\r\n- Design: **[Black Dashboard](https://app-generator.dev/docs/templates/bootstrap/black-dashboard.html)** (Bootstrap)\r\n- **Sections Covered**: \r\n  - `Admin Section`, reserved for `superusers`\r\n  - `All pages` managed by `Django.contrib.AUTH`\r\n  - `Registration` page\r\n  - `Misc pages`: colors, icons, typography, blank-page \r\n  \r\n<br />\r\n\r\n### Build a Starter with [Django App Generator - Black Design](https://app-generator.dev/tools/django-generator/black/)\r\n\r\n- Access the [App Generator](https://app-generator.dev/tools/django-generator/) page\r\n- Select **Black Dashboard** as the preferred design\r\n- (Optional) Design Database: edit models and fields\r\n- (Optional) Edit the fields for the extended user model\r\n- (Optional) Enable OAuth for GitHub\r\n- (Optional) Add Celery (async tasks)\r\n- (Optional) Enable Dynamic API Module\r\n- Docker Scripts\r\n- Render CI/Cd Scripts\r\n\r\n**The generated Django project is available as a ZIP Archive and also uploaded to GitHub.**\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n![Django Black Dashboard - Modern template for Django Admin Section crafted on top of a modern Bootstrap Design.](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/51070104/196730732-dda1794b-93ce-48cb-bc5c-182411495512.png)\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n## [Black Dashboard PRO Version](https://app-generator.dev/product/black-dashboard-pro/django/)\r\n\r\n> The premium version provides more features, priority on support, and is more often updated - [Live Demo](https://django-black-pro.onrender.com).\r\n\r\n- **Simple, Easy-to-Extend** Codebase\r\n- **Black Dashboard** Design - PRO Version\r\n- Bootstrap 4 CSS\r\n- **OAuth** - Github\r\n- **Extended User Profile**\r\n- **API** via DRF \r\n- **Charts** via ApexJS \r\n- **Celery** (async tasks)\r\n- **Deployment-Ready** for Render \r\n\r\n![Django Black PRO - Premium Django starter built with Black Dashboard design from Creative-Tim](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/63c1ea5b-6c8b-4e67-8e07-156c3e06895f)\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n---\r\n**[Django Black Dashboard](https://app-generator.dev/docs/products/django-libs/theme-black-dashboard.html)** - Modern Django Admin Interface provided by **[App-Generator](https://app-generator.dev)**\r\n\r\n\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "setup", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "setup.README", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "admin_black.migrations.0001_initial", "documentation": ["Generated by Django 3.1.1 on 2020-11-02 18:06"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "admin_black.migrations.0001_initial.Migration", "bases": ["migrations.Migration"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "admin_black.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.initial", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "admin_black.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.dependencies", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "admin_black.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.operations", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "admin_black.migrations", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "admin_black.templatetags", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "admin_black.templatetags.admin_black", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "admin_black.templatetags.admin_black.clean_text", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "value", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "admin_black.templatetags.admin_black.checkbox", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "value", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "admin_black.templatetags.admin_black.admin_get_menu", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "context", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "admin_black.templatetags.admin_black.get_direction", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "context", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "admin_black.templatetags.a